      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this dependable daily driver that's ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a practical, no-nonsense vehicle that still has plenty of life left for your commutes and errands!",
