    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently runs roughly and will likely need a full overhaul, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping. Visually, the body has several deep rust spots along the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the clear coat is peeling across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. It is not currently in roadworthy condition and will need to be towed.",
