    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a reliable and well-cared-for vehicle in good condition. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only moderate wear on the driver's side upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, it remains in excellent shape with a consistent service history, offering a smooth ride and dependable performance for its next owner.",
